snippet.title: Roma and Papa play a funny story
snippet.description:
Video with Roma and his Dad. Roma and Papa play and sing nursery rhymes. Little Roma has been eating sugar and lies to his daddy about this. After singing the nursery rhyme, you have a great opportunity to talk with the kids about lies.
